description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'Reverse Climb Cool-Down' from the channel Mac Evans.
The workout falls under Cool-down/Cool-down.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The The Reboot Workout vibe means Deep stretch, low stress, total-body refresh. This is especially good for Recovery days, stress relief, post-travel stiffness. The The Endorphin Wave vibe means Elevated energy, feel-good movement, steady build. This is especially good for When you want a challenging but steady burn..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Prioritizing bringing down your heart rate with Mac in this extended cool-down.

Max rhythm: 24, Format: Reverse Climb...
